18210630,https://www.airbnb.com/rooms/18210630,Bayfront Mission Beach Oasis,"Nestled on the beautiful bayfront in South Mission Beach, our fully furnished vacation rental offers everything you need to enjoy your trip. The home includes boogie boards, beach towels, A/C and TV in bedroom, dishware, BBQ, Satellite TV with movie channels, and complimentary Wi-Fi. All you need is your toothbrush and bathing suit! Come enjoy all that Mission Beach and San Diego has to offer in your own beach apartment, for less than the price of a hotel.",The bedroom has one queen bed and a futon.  Other sleeping options are the large couch in the living room. We can also provide an air mattress.,"Nestled on the beautiful bayfront in South Mission Beach, our fully furnished vacation rental offers everything you need to enjoy your trip. The home includes boogie boards, beach towels, A/C and TV in bedroom, dishware, BBQ, Satellite TV with movie channels, and complimentary Wi-Fi. All you need is your toothbrush and bathing suit! Come enjoy all that Mission Beach and San Diego has to offer in your own beach apartment, for less than the price of a hotel. The bedroom has one queen bed and a futon.  Other sleeping options are the large couch in the living room. We can also provide an air mattress. For stays longer than 30 days, I require a deposit in the amount of one month's rent to be paid offline due 60 days prior to arrival. This is a recently acquired property. Please view my profile to see the positive reviews from other listings to get an understanding of how I run my business. I am a Superhost, and you will be well taken care of. Please note that the patio that is pictured is s",,"For stays longer than 30 days, I require a deposit in the amount of one month's rent to be paid offline due 60 days prior to arrival. This is a recently acquired property. Please view my profile to see the positive reviews from other listings to get an understanding of how I run my business. I am a Superhost, and you will be well taken care of. Please note that the patio that is pictured is solely for the use of our guests and it fronts Bayside Walk and the Bay. It is not contiguous to the unit (which is a guesthouse above and behind the main house).  To access the patio you need to head downstairs and enter the patio from the bayside of the main home off the front gate.",,,,,,8336938,https://www.airbnb.com/users/show/8336938,Vacation Rentals By Aaron,8/23/2013,"San Diego, California, United States","Native San Diegan...Reformed attorney, turned life coach and property manager...father of 2 wonderful ladies and married to the coolest woman on the planet for the last 25 years...love sports (competitive and participatory), reading, dancing, travel and anytime I get to spend on my bicycle. 

Since I have only been on ABB I only have a few reviews...however I have been on Flip key and Home away for a much longer stretch and have a significantly larger number of reviews there so please take a look at them if you would like more feedback on what it is like to stay with us at one of our units.",within an hour,100%,,t,La Jolla,63,63,t,t,"San Diego, CA, United States",Mission Beach,Mission Bay,San Diego,CA,92109,San Diego,"San Diego, CA",US,United States,32.7718,-117.2497,t,Condominium,Entire home/apt,6,1,1,3,Real Bed,"{bbb""}",,$340.00 ,$340.00 ,$500.00 ,$120.00 ,4,$25.00 ,2,1125,19,38,5/30/2017,7/29/2019,Average,f,t,f,strict_14_with_grace_period,f,f
21513447,https://www.airbnb.com/rooms/21513447,Two Bedroom Furnished Apartments in East Village,"We invite you to stay with us and live the California dream! Welcome to your modern 2 bedroom apartment in San Diego's exciting East Village - 130 blocks of great bars, dining, boutique shopping, galleries, live music venues, luxury living! Just minutes from popular hot spot Gaslamp Quarter,  this fully furnished apartment with fully equipped kitchen, balcony and breathtaking city views is perfect for your short or long-term, vacation or corporate stay.","Just SOME of the premium services you will have access to during your stay include: •	24-hour front desk •	Express check-in/check-out •	 Private check-in/check-out •	Airport shuttle service •	ATM/cash machine on site •	1 + king bed + 1 sofa bed •	Complimentary fresh linens & towels •	Complimentary essential toiletries •	Heating and air-conditioning •	Complimentary fresh linens & towels •	Complimentary essential toiletries & hair dryer •	Walk in closet •	Washer & dryer facilities •	Wheelchair friendly •	Approved pets welcome PLEASE NOTE:  The images shown are a representation and may not look exactly the same as the unit booked as we have multiple units within the property.","We invite you to stay with us and live the California dream! Welcome to your modern 2 bedroom apartment in San Diego's exciting East Village - 130 blocks of great bars, dining, boutique shopping, galleries, live music venues, luxury living! Just minutes from popular hot spot Gaslamp Quarter,  this fully furnished apartment with fully equipped kitchen, balcony and breathtaking city views is perfect for your short or long-term, vacation or corporate stay. Just SOME of the premium services you will have access to during your stay include: •	24-hour front desk •	Express check-in/check-out •	 Private check-in/check-out •	Airport shuttle service •	ATM/cash machine on site •	1 + king bed + 1 sofa bed •	Complimentary fresh linens & towels •	Complimentary essential toiletries •	Heating and air-conditioning •	Complimentary fresh linens & towels •	Complimentary essential toiletries & hair dryer •	Walk in closet •	Washer & dryer facilities •	Wheelchair friendly •	Approved pets welcome PLEASE NOTE:","FOR YOUR EVERYDAY GROCERY ITEMS AND DAILY NEEDS •	Albertsons Grocery Store (0.1 miles) •	Albertsons Pharmacy (0.1 miles) •	Ralph’s (organic grocery store) (0.9 miles) •	Grocery Outlet Bargain Market (0.3 miles)  FABULOUS DINING  •	BESHOCK Ramen (0.1 miles) •	Lotus Thai Cuisine (0.3 miles) •	Bud & Rob's New Orleans Bistro (0.6 miles)  •	Mariscos Mi Gusto Es (0.4 miles) •	The Mission (0.3 miles) •	Fuego (0.4 miles) •	Basic (0.4 miles) •	Ciro's Pizzeria (0.5 miles) •	Mariscos El Pulpo (1.0 miles) •	Tajima Ramen East Village (0.6 miles) •	Krispy Krunchy Chicken (0.2 miles) •	Hodad's Downtown (0.7 miles) are just SOME of your delicious dining options!  FABULOUS SHOPPING AWAITS YOU! •	Westfield Horton Plaza (1.1 miles) •	Seaport Village (1.3 miles) •	The Headquarters at Seaport (1.3 miles) •	Fashion Alley (9.4 miles) •	Coronado Plaza (4.5 miles) AMAZING NIGHTLIFE & ENTERTAINMENT – so many theaters, bars and more nearby! •	Spreckels Theatre (1.1 miles) •	Theater Box (0.6 miles) •	Rooftop Cine","Kindly note that our check-in time is 3pm and check-out is at 11am.  Unfortunately, we cannot guarantee early check-ins before 3pm.  Check-ins after 9pm will incur a late fee of $25. Please be aware this is a self-serviced apartment and therefore we do not provide food or drink items however for your convenience Albertsons Grocery Store & Pharmacy, Ralph’s (organic grocery store) and Grocery Outlet Bargain Market are all located nearby for your daily items and personal needs. For your convenience essential toiletries such as shampoo/conditioner, soap and toilet paper are provided on arrival however additional supplies are the responsibility of the guest. All guests must call or notify the property at least an hour prior to arrival so we can ensure that the unit is ready to be occupied. A $250 security deposit will only be charged to the guest should there be any damages in the unit upon check out. All properties are strictly non-smoking. All special requests are subject to availability","GETTING AROUND San Diego has accessible and affordable public transit systems that include trolleys, buses, trains and shuttles. SAN DIEGO INTERNATIONAL AIRPORT TO OUR SAN DIEGO APT: 1.	Starting point San Diego International Airport, 3225 N Harbor Dr, San Diego, CA 92101, USA 2.	Head east on N Harbor Dr towards McCain Rd 2.9 mi 3.	Turn left onto W Broadway 0.1 mi 4.	Turn right at the 1st cross street onto Pacific Hwy 0.2 mi 5.	Turn left onto W G St 6.	Pass by Comfort Inn Gaslamp Convention Center (on the left in 0.7 mi) 1.1 mi 7.	Turn right onto 14th St 381 ft 8.	Turn left onto Market St 9.	 Destination will be on the left 338 ft 1450 Market St San Diego, CA 92101, USA","Our guests enjoy access to our: •	Business center  •	Fitness center •	Barbecue facilities & fire pit •	Saline pool w/beach towels •	Spa  •	Bicycle rental service •	Bike & surfboard storage •	Common lounge •	Clubhouse with folding glass windows •	Courtyard area •	Dog run •	Electric vehicle charging stations •	Controlled Access Parking •	Pet wash  •	Postal/Mailbox service  •	Private storage available •	Rooftop deck","Guest satisfaction is very important to us.  Our friendly Pelican Stay staff are ready to assist our guests every step of the way - from booking to check out.  Our customer service representatives are on standby 24/7 via phone, chat and/or email to answer your questions and assist with inquiries. Please note that while we will endeavor to accommodate, all Special Requests are subject to availability and additional charges may apply.","1) Due to previous incidents, a minimum age requirement of 21+ has been implemented.  Guests under the age of 21 are welcome as long as they are accompanied by a parent or guardian. 2) To prevent plumbing issues, please place things like sanity napkins in the sanitary bin provided in the bathroom.   3) Complaints of excessive noise and unruly behavior will unfortunately result in you being asked to leave immediately.  Please consider your respective guests and surroundings. 4) Check-in is 3pm, and check-out is by 11am.  Arriving slightly earlier, or want that extra hour to sleep? It should be fine, but please check with us first. 5) While we do a thorough professional cleaning between each guest stay, prior to leaving, we kindly ask that you clean and put away any dishes or kitchenware used and put any dirty towels in the hamper. It helps us get through our cleaning process quicker and allows us to keep cleaning costs down for you and future guests. 6) We understand that accidents happ",,4140161,https://www.airbnb.com/users/show/4140161,Corporate,11/13/2012,"Jersey City, New Jersey, United States",Providing short and long term stay vacation rental.,within an hour,100%,,f,Little Havana,280,280,t,t,"San Diego, CA, United States",East Village,East Village,San Diego,CA,92101,San Diego,"San Diego, CA",US,United States,32.71278,-117.15222,f,Apartment,Entire home/apt,6,2,2,2,Real Bed,"{TV,Wifi,""Air conditioning"",Pool,Kitchen,""Free parking on premises"",Gym,Elevator,Heating,""Family/kid friendly"",Washer,Dryer,""Smoke detector"",""Fire extinguisher"",Essentials,Shampoo,""Lock on bedroom door"",Hangers,""Hair dryer"",Iron,""Laptop friendly workspace"",""Private entrance"",""Host greets you""}",,$499.00 ,$499.00 ,$250.00 ,$105.00 ,1,$0.00 ,7,1125,12,24,12/3/2017,10/24/2018,Average,f,t,f,strict_14_with_grace_period,f,f
15376224,https://www.airbnb.com/rooms/15376224,Downtown San Diego Studio With All You Need,"My studio is located in Downtown - Cortez Hill. Step outside and you can walk to many restaurants and shops. The Convention Center (Comic Con), Gaslamp Headquarters, Balboa Park, Horton Plaza, famous well known Donut Bar,  Petco Park, and San Diego Symphony are all within walking distance.",Chalkboard walls Private balcony Breakfast bars Electric oven Frost-free refrigerator with ice-maker Microwave Fully-equipped kitchen include dishwasher Garbage disposal Modern hard surface flooring Mini blinds Accent walls Spacious closets Air conditioning ENERGY STAR ® appliances Sustainable apartment plumbing fixtures and HVAC equipment,"My studio is located in Downtown - Cortez Hill. Step outside and you can walk to many restaurants and shops. The Convention Center (Comic Con), Gaslamp Headquarters, Balboa Park, Horton Plaza, famous well known Donut Bar,  Petco Park, and San Diego Symphony are all within walking distance. Chalkboard walls Private balcony Breakfast bars Electric oven Frost-free refrigerator with ice-maker Microwave Fully-equipped kitchen include dishwasher Garbage disposal Modern hard surface flooring Mini blinds Accent walls Spacious closets Air conditioning ENERGY STAR ® appliances Sustainable apartment plumbing fixtures and HVAC equipment Please note that i'm still updating the listing, so i'll have additional information on it soon.  The entire studio in for rent. It has a queen size bed and for additional quests there is the option of the the black sofa that becomes a a bed. Chalkboard walls Private balcony Breakfast bars Electric oven Frost-free refrigerator with ice-maker Microwave Fully-equippe",Chalkboard walls Private balcony Breakfast bars Electric oven Frost-free refrigerator with ice-maker Microwave Fully-equipped kitchen include dishwasher Garbage disposal Modern hard surface flooring Mini blinds Accent walls Spacious closets Air conditioning ENERGY STAR ® appliances Sustainable apartment plumbing fixtures and HVAC equipment,"State-of-the-art fitness center with cardio and strength equipment Basketball court Lighted tennis court Relaxing hot tub Pool-side BBQ area with lounge seating and cabanas Chill space with big-screen TV, Kinect and wet bar Loft lounge with comfortable seating and communal table On-site laundry facilities Elevators available for your convenience Gated entrance with controlled access Sustainable lighting techniques to reduce energy consumption Walking distance to Gaslamp District Balboa and Petco Park  On-site deli and market Walking distance to Commuter/Light Rail station Located near public transportation","I'm within a 10 minute walk to Gaslamp and 0.5 miles away from Horton Plaza. I'm in Cortez Hills and per the map the distance is 1.2 miles away from the convention center. It states an average of a 27 minute walk and 7 minutes by car, which would probably be longer than a 7 minute drive due to the traffic. Downtown now offers the option to rent electric scooters and bikes. Here's more details about the Limebike  (Website hidden by Airbnb) Also, you have the option on using FRED the free ride, (Website hidden by Airbnb) For both of these options you will need to download the apps. If you were to walk from my apartment to the convention center, it'll also be a great experience as many people are walking around in customs and taking pictures, etc.  I'm  a  5 minute walk away  from the famous Donut Bar (Website hidden by Airbnb)","Please note that i'm still updating the listing, so i'll have additional information on it soon.  The entire studio in for rent. It has a queen size bed and for additional quests there is the option of the the black sofa that becomes a a bed.",,,,2921712,https://www.airbnb.com/users/show/2921712,Stacy,7/13/2012,"San Diego, California, United States","I am a healthcare administration professional that works long hours and I'm not home on the weekends and I travel a lot in which, I use my apartment for approximately 25% of the month. I love my place when I am home, but when I'm away I would love for others to enjoy what my apartment along with the area of Downtown has to offer. If you plan on staying longer than a weekend (during the week, week, or month), please contact me for arrangements. ",,,,f,,1,1,t,t,"San Diego, CA, United States",Core-Columbia,Cortez Hill,San Diego,CA,92101,San Diego,"San Diego, CA",US,United States,32.7193,-117.15512,f,Condominium,Entire home/apt,2,1,0,1,Real Bed,"{TV,Wifi,""Air conditioning"",Pool,Kitchen,""Paid parking off premises"",Gym,Elevator,""Hot tub"",Heating,Washer,Dryer,""Smoke detector"",Essentials,Shampoo,Hangers,Iron,""Hot water"",Microwave,Refrigerator,Dishwasher,""Dishes and silverware"",""Cooking basics"",Oven,Stove,""BBQ grill"",""Patio or balcony"",Other}",,$175.00 ,$350.00 ,$0.00 ,$100.00 ,2,$50.00 ,2,7,2,4,7/9/2018,7/22/2018,Very High,f,f,f,moderate,t,t
6255485,https://www.airbnb.com/rooms/6255485,Gorgeous Private 2 BD Home in PB,"Remodeled two bedroom home in quiet Pacific Beach neighborhood just 5 blocks from the ocean, not right in front of the ocean. We truly hope you enjoy your stay!","We spent a lot of time turning this space into a home away from home for our guests. This quiet two bedroom house has one completely remodeled bathroom, a huge gourmet kitchen, custom-made beds, and plenty of amenities. We truly hope you enjoy your stay!","Remodeled two bedroom home in quiet Pacific Beach neighborhood just 5 blocks from the ocean, not right in front of the ocean. We truly hope you enjoy your stay! We spent a lot of time turning this space into a home away from home for our guests. This quiet two bedroom house has one completely remodeled bathroom, a huge gourmet kitchen, custom-made beds, and plenty of amenities. We truly hope you enjoy your stay! You will have access to the entire home. Minimal interaction as this is a private home but we live close and will remain available if our guests have any questions. This house is located in the quiet area of Pacific Beach, just 5 blocks from the ocean not right in front of the ocean, shopping and restaurants are close. There is a one car driveway in front of the house and free street parking. Things to do in San diego  https://www.airbnb.com/things-to-do/san-diego","This house is located in the quiet area of Pacific Beach, just 5 blocks from the ocean not right in front of the ocean, shopping and restaurants are close.",Things to do in San diego  https://www.airbnb.com/things-to-do/san-diego,There is a one car driveway in front of the house and free street parking.,You will have access to the entire home.,Minimal interaction as this is a private home but we live close and will remain available if our guests have any questions.,"One day booking allowed only to fill a gap. Please treat our home with the respect and care you would like if it were your own. Do no throw anything but paper in the toilet (no feminine protections), drains are very small. Trash collection is on Monday morning, please put the trash cans outside on Sunday. No pets. Smoking outside ONLY. Quiet hours 9pm to 8am.",,7806201,https://www.airbnb.com/users/show/7806201,Marie,7/29/2013,"San Diego, California, United States",We are a French couple and have lived in San Diego for the past 7 years. We have enjoyed travelling extensively with our three daughters and cannot wait to share our beautiful home with our guests! ,within an hour,100%,,f,,1,1,t,t,"San Diego, CA, United States",Pacific Beach,Pacific Beach,San Diego,CA,92109,San Diego,"San Diego, CA",US,United States,32.79838,-117.23269,f,Cottage,Entire home/apt,6,1,2,4,Real Bed,"{TV,""Cable TV"",Internet,Wifi,""Air conditioning"",Kitchen,""Free parking on premises"",""Smoking allowed"",""Free street parking"",""Indoor fireplace"",Heating,""Family/kid friendly"",Washer,Dryer,""Smoke detector"",""Carbon monoxide detector"",""First aid kit"",""Safety card"",""Fire extinguisher"",Essentials,Shampoo,""24-hour check-in"",Hangers,""Hair dryer"",Iron,""Laptop friendly workspace"",""Self check-in"",Lockbox,""Private entrance"",Bathtub,""Baby bath"",""High chair"",""Children’s books and toys"",""Pack ’n Play/travel crib"",""Hot water"",""Bed linens"",""Extra pillows and blankets"",Microwave,""Coffee maker"",Refrigerator,Dishwasher,""Dishes and silverware"",""Cooking basics"",Oven,Stove,""BBQ grill"",""Garden or backyard"",""Beach essentials"",""Luggage dropoff allowed"",""Long term stays allowed"",""Well-lit path to entrance"",""No stairs or steps to enter"",""Accessible-height bed"",""No stairs or steps to enter""}",,$155.00 ,$155.00 ,$300.00 ,$110.00 ,4,$25.00 ,1,1125,231,462,5/27/2015,8/16/2019,High,f,f,f,strict_14_with_grace_period,f,f
17154343,https://www.airbnb.com/rooms/17154343,Ultimate Downtown San Diego 2BR/2Bath Experience!,"Located in the heart of San Diego’s Downtown Little Italy neighborhood, our beautiful and new 1000 sqft apartment is the home you’ve been waiting for. Features exquisite queen beds, 6 person Venetian dining area, full kitchen w/many essentials, in unit washer/dryer, 3 HDTV's w/ 200+ cable channels, WIFI, infinity pool & jacuzzi overlooking the bay, fitness center, club house, yoga studio, computer room, 2 free parking spots & more! Perfect for couples, business travelers, & families!","Experience the energy and spirit of San Diego from within its most vibrant neighborhood. Wake up to the love of the city and enjoy gorgeous San Diego bay views while having easy access everywhere. Take in the coastal resort experience from the city's most walkable and modern urban village. Designer furnished, impeccably styled amenities, and a coveted location experience awaits you. Welcome to the beautiful life. Outside the building, you are literally in the middle of hundreds of popular and loved restaurants, cafes, lounges, and attractions. You'll also be just an 8 minute drive to San Diego’s Gaslamp District.  The apartment has all brand new flooring, counter tops, appliances, electronics, and furniture.  You have the entirely new 1000 square foot apartment all to yourself.  It is on the 3rd floor of the building. It is safe, upscale, breathtaking, and yet close to everything in town!  Bedrooms & Bedding: Dual master bedrooms! The two master bedrooms each have a queen bed and each ","Located in the heart of San Diego’s Downtown Little Italy neighborhood, our beautiful and new 1000 sqft apartment is the home you’ve been waiting for. Features exquisite queen beds, 6 person Venetian dining area, full kitchen w/many essentials, in unit washer/dryer, 3 HDTV's w/ 200+ cable channels, WIFI, infinity pool & jacuzzi overlooking the bay, fitness center, club house, yoga studio, computer room, 2 free parking spots & more! Perfect for couples, business travelers, & families! Experience the energy and spirit of San Diego from within its most vibrant neighborhood. Wake up to the love of the city and enjoy gorgeous San Diego bay views while having easy access everywhere. Take in the coastal resort experience from the city's most walkable and modern urban village. Designer furnished, impeccably styled amenities, and a coveted location experience awaits you. Welcome to the beautiful life. Outside the building, you are literally in the middle of hundreds of popular and loved restaur","HOT SPOTS: San Diego International Airport (2.2 miles) - 6 minute drive San Diego Convention Center. (1.4 miles) - 10 minute drive. Little Italy Famous Restaurants/Shopping - Outside The Building. Gaslamp Restaurants, Bars, & Clubs - 2 minute drive. Manchester Grand Hyatt - 5 minute drive. Seaport Village Shopping & Restaurants - 5 minute drive. USS Midway Statue - 5 minute drive. Famous ""Soldier Kiss"" Statue - 5 minute drive. Petco Park Stadium - 10 minute drive  Sea World - 15 minute drive San Diego Zoo - 15 minute drive.  Qualcomm Stadium - 10-15 minute drive San Diego Beaches - 10 minute drive Over 100 years of history have shaped the streets of our neighborhood. Beginning with Italian immigrants in the early 1900's who built Little Italy's homes and businesses around a thriving fishing industry, all the way to today's vibrant village of authentic restaurants, boutique stores, modern residences and well-kept streets and parks. Everyone's go-to spot. Date-night. Craft beers and cock","The Manchester Grand Hyatt, located 1 mile away, has a 2 bedroom high suite similar to ours for over $1000/night. Mama Mia! The pool is not heated.","TROLLY METRO & BUSES CLOSE BY LYFT: The best way to get around if you're not driving is via Lyft. Lyft is an App on your phone that let you order a private upscale taxi and have it arrive within minutes to wherever you are. All payments are automatic and you can see where your taxi is at all times. You can even review the route the driver took, rate your driver, or contact Lyft's support team in case you are not satisfied. Service is superb and costs less than city run taxis. To sign up, download the LYFT app on your Iphone or Android phone. Enter code DAVID9548 to receive a discount.","The entire apartment is yours. In fact, ""The world is yours!""",Check In Service: My assistant/concierge will contact you via email or telephone 2 days before your arrival and set up an exact time to drop off the keys and show you around the apartment in person.  You will have the whole place to yourself. You can reach me or my assistants on Airbnb or via telephone if you need anything. I want to make sure you have an amazing experience.,"NOISE & DECORUM This is not a party location or hotel. This is a residential building with long term neighbors who enjoy peace and quiet. Please keep the noise level to a minimum after 10pm. Please be very respectful in the hallways, amenity areas, and public areas in and around the building. If there is loud noise or music from our unit, the entire security deposit is forfeited, there will be a noise violation fine, and you may be asked to leave. Loud noise and music is not allowed in the unit at any time. Thank you for your cooperation.  MINIMUM AGE Minimum age to book is 21 years of age.  SMOKING Smoking is not allowed in our home, patios, and public areas; including outdoor areas. Evidence of smoking of any kind, including Marijuana, will be fined at $500 on your Airbnb account.  CHECK IN/OUT •Early check In: If the apartment is ready before 3pm, we may be able to do an early check in for you. Your check in assistant/home concierge will know if that's possible, 24 hours before your",,71872719,https://www.airbnb.com/users/show/71872719,Abe,5/13/2016,"San Diego, California, United States"," I've decided to leave the corporate world and instead; travel the world!
To help pay for my adventures and new businesses, I've listed my beautiful lofts in the cities I visit the most on Airbnb. I've lived, worked, played, and fallen in love with these cities my whole life and now I'm more than willing to help you have the best trip you've ever had. I use a professional property management customer service team to help me and a professional cleaning crew to take care of my units. You are in great hands. 

Remember, don't just visit here, live here! You are not a tourist, you're now family. That is what Airbnb is all about.  My places books up extremely fast so please book today! Talk to you soon 

Your fellow Airbnb traveling friend! 
Abe
 ",within an hour,100%,,t,Marina,15,15,t,t,"San Diego, CA, United States",Little Italy,Little Italy,San Diego,CA,92103,San Diego,"San Diego, CA",US,United States,32.72485,-117.16877,f,Apartment,Entire home/apt,6,2,2,3,Real Bed,"{TV,""Cable TV"",Internet,Wifi,""Air conditioning"",Pool,Kitchen,""Free parking on premises"",Gym,Elevator,""Hot tub"",Heating,""Family/kid friendly"",Washer,Dryer,""Smoke detector"",""Carbon monoxide detector"",""First aid kit"",""Fire extinguisher"",Essentials,Shampoo,Hangers,""Hair dryer"",Iron,""Laptop friendly workspace"",""High chair"",""Children’s books and toys"",""Pack ’n Play/travel crib"",""Room-darkening shades"",""Hot water"",""Bed linens"",""Extra pillows and blankets"",""Ethernet connection"",""Pocket wifi"",Microwave,""Coffee maker"",Refrigerator,Dishwasher,""Dishes and silverware"",""Cooking basics"",Oven,Stove,""Single level home"",""Patio or balcony"",""Luggage dropoff allowed"",""Well-lit path to entrance"",""Host greets you""}",,$249.00 ,$498.00 ,$129.00 ,$129.00 ,6,$300.00 ,2,1125,137,274,2/22/2017,8/11/2019,Very High,f,t,f,moderate,f,f
,https://www.airbnb.com/rooms/4857549,1 Bedroom in Lux Dual Master Apt.,"Very comfortable and private bedroom (1) and bathroom in a 2 bed, 2 bath luxury apartment.  You will have apartment to yourself - I will not be present.  However, there is not access to my bedroom or bathroom.","1 double/full bed 1 memory foam mattress Full bathroom adjoining that bedroom 2 couches (1 in your bedroom and can be slept on) TV with ATT cable Wifi Internet computer desk and chair Diswasher Laudry in-suite Overall, your group could do 4 people depending on sleeping arrangement. (2 in bed, 1 on couch, 1 on memory foam) Guests have will have full access to the kitchen and access to the apartment's pool and community BBQs.  There is also a washer and dryer for your use in the apartment itself.","Very comfortable and private bedroom (1) and bathroom in a 2 bed, 2 bath luxury apartment.  You will have apartment to yourself - I will not be present.  However, there is not access to my bedroom or bathroom. 1 double/full bed 1 memory foam mattress Full bathroom adjoining that bedroom 2 couches (1 in your bedroom and can be slept on) TV with ATT cable Wifi Internet computer desk and chair Diswasher Laudry in-suite Overall, your group could do 4 people depending on sleeping arrangement. (2 in bed, 1 on couch, 1 on memory foam) Guests have will have full access to the kitchen and access to the apartment's pool and community BBQs.  There is also a washer and dryer for your use in the apartment itself. Guests have will have full access to the common area, kitchen, and access to the apartment's pool and community BBQs.  There is also a washer and dryer for your use in the apartment itself. Guests can use the fridge and kitchen as they please.  I will often have some basic food or condieme","This apartment is in an ideal location being: 10 minutes from the airport 10 minutes to Pacific Beach 8 minutes to Ocean Beach 5 minutes to Sea World 5 minutes to Fashion Valley Mall 15 minutes to the Gaslamp District These are driving or cab times. You can take the Trolley to downtown, the malls in Mission Valley, Qualcomm Stadium, SDSU etc. via the Trolley stop that is literally just out the door. There are several food services all under a 5 minute walk from the apartment including: Starbucks 7-11 Carl's Junior Subway Jamba Juice Dominos Pizza And several other local stores/shops This is truly a great, convenient, and central location for most everything you may want and need to do during your stay in San Diego.",,,"Guests have will have full access to the common area, kitchen, and access to the apartment's pool and community BBQs.  There is also a washer and dryer for your use in the apartment itself. Guests can use the fridge and kitchen as they please.  I will often have some basic food or condiements available for your use to add to your meals if you plan to cook here.  You are welcome to utilize the kitchen (or BBQs) with groceries you buy for the other meals. I have cable TV and you will have access to both the Wi-fi and a TV of some sort.  I also have an Xbox and it is a smart TV where you may utilize your various subscriptions (Netflix, Hulu, etc.) or watch a DVD with.  I imagine you should be out enjoying San Diego, but I can accomodate these features.",I will not be present during your stay.,"No smoking.  No hard drugs.  No parties or afterparties.  If you go to the beach, please try to prevent as much sand from coming back into the apartment.",,12575162,https://www.airbnb.com/users/show/12575162,Dan,2/25/2014,"San Diego, California, United States",MBA Graduate Student in San Diego.  Canadian and American.  Buckeye.  Workout and enjoy sports in my free time.,,,,f,Morena,2,2,t,t,"San Diego, CA, United States",Morena,Moreno Mission,San Diego,CA,92110,San Diego,"San Diego, CA",US,United States,32.76385,-117.19694,t,Apartment,Entire home/apt,4,1,1,1,Real Bed,"{TV,""Cable TV"",Internet,Wifi,""Air conditioning"",Pool,Kitchen,""Free parking on premises"",Gym,Elevator,""Hot tub"",Heating,""Family/kid friendly"",Washer,Dryer,""Smoke detector"",""Carbon monoxide detector"",Essentials,Shampoo}",,$71.00 ,$142.00 ,$100.00 ,$7.00 ,1,$5.00 ,2,1125,2,4,12/27/2014,10/4/2015,Very High,f,f,f,moderate,f,f
24759912,https://www.airbnb.com/rooms/24759912,Cozy Retreat Two Blocks from the Ocean and Cliffs,"Just a few blocks from the ocean and the gorgeous Sunset Cliffs, we welcome you to unwind and enjoy the SoCal lifestyle like a local in our cozy and private guest bedroom. Complete with private ensuite bathroom and French doors that open up to a private patio. You will have the entire lower level of our home to yourself along with a private entrance, so it's like you have the entire place to yourself.",,"Just a few blocks from the ocean and the gorgeous Sunset Cliffs, we welcome you to unwind and enjoy the SoCal lifestyle like a local in our cozy and private guest bedroom. Complete with private ensuite bathroom and French doors that open up to a private patio. You will have the entire lower level of our home to yourself along with a private entrance, so it's like you have the entire place to yourself. Guests will have access to the guest bedroom with ensuite bath and private patio. The garage is located on the first floor adjacent to the private room. You may access to use the washing and drying machine should you need to do laundry. Our living space is on the second floor is not accessible for guests therefore no kitchen access is available. We do have small fridge along with coffee maker and electric kettle available for guests in the room. We live on the second floor, but respect your privacy and always available should you need anything. Ocean Beach is one of the most quintessentia","Ocean Beach is one of the most quintessential Southern California beach towns. Laid back, eclectic, and super friendly. Live like a local and explore all this amazing peninsula has to offer, from the Sunset Cliffs Natural Park, to the surfer lined beaches of Ocean Beach. The area has an array of local independent shops, restaurants, breweries, and bars, all with their own unique offerings. We'd be happy to provide some of our favorite local spots for you to explore.","We have two very friendly and curious dogs who love to greet our guests by barking from the second floor, which means you may hear them when you come and go from the home. Don't worry, we are completely used to it, so don't feel like you need to be tiptoe around, We also live on the second floor, so you may hear footsteps and paws clicking from above.",The center of OB on Newport Ave is only a 10-15 minute walk or few minute drive from house. Downtown San Diego and the Airport is only 10-15 minute drive away. Public transit is also available with the bus stop 1 block away. We have a smart car available to rent should you need something something to get around town in. It's so easy to find parking spots!,Guests will have access to the guest bedroom with ensuite bath and private patio. The garage is located on the first floor adjacent to the private room. You may access to use the washing and drying machine should you need to do laundry. Our living space is on the second floor is not accessible for guests therefore no kitchen access is available. We do have small fridge along with coffee maker and electric kettle available for guests in the room.,"We live on the second floor, but respect your privacy and always available should you need anything.",- We prefer no shoes in the house please. - Please observe quiet hours from 10PM-9AM. - The second floor is our living space and is closed off to guests.,,14635886,https://www.airbnb.com/users/show/14635886,Peter & Diana,4/23/2014,"San Diego, California, United States","We love to travel and meet people from all over the world.  One of our favorite trips was to Cuzco, Peru where we stayed with one the best Airbnb hosts who was so hospitable and welcoming. The human connection of staying with a local host who knows the city creates an experience you cannot get from any hotel. This is why we decided to become Airbnb hosts.

We would love to have you create your own experiences here with us and invite you to book one of our properties. We would be happy to make recommendations to some of our favorite local hikes, restaurants, and attractions. 

When we aren't working or traveling, we love hanging out with our two dogs; a Welsh Terrier named Moose, and a Corgi-dachshund mix named Melo. 

