23000738,https://www.airbnb.com/rooms/23000738,Penthouse escape- Ocean View w/  balcony,"5 minutes to airport -  5 minutes to down town  6 minutes to ballpark / Comic-Con  This Penthouse is an ideal choice for a luxurious and convenient stay.  With all new appliances, a state of the art kitchen, and modern amenities, this place will feel like home once you step into the unit.  Overlooking the harbor and downtown, this space has 3 balconies on which to enjoy the beautiful weather, sunrises and sunsets. I hope you enjoy!","This is a luxury condo with cathedral ceilings, custom furnishings, and a cool industrial / mid-century design that will make you feel like you stepped into a magazine. It’s a true penthouse spanning the whole top floor of the building. Here are a few things you will find if you stay here:  - Chef's kitchen with a gas range stove and grill. Complete with dishes, cutlery, and appliances (vitamix blender, rice cooker, toaster, hot water maker, coffee maker, le crusset wok, casserole dish, and pan)   - Den with a fully stocked library   - 2 West facing balconies, one with a small garden, both with seating (great for watching the sunset)  - 1 East facing balcony, great for watching the sunrise  - Reading nook that is perfect for relaxing and watching the boats on the harbor  - Baby grand piano  - 4k OLED TV  - Netflix, Hulu, Amazon Video  - Hue lighting throughout house  - Speaker system throughout house  - 2016 washer and dryer  - Triple stream shower","5 minutes to airport -  5 minutes to down town  6 minutes to ballpark / Comic-Con  This Penthouse is an ideal choice for a luxurious and convenient stay.  With all new appliances, a state of the art kitchen, and modern amenities, this place will feel like home once you step into the unit.  Overlooking the harbor and downtown, this space has 3 balconies on which to enjoy the beautiful weather, sunrises and sunsets. I hope you enjoy! This is a luxury condo with cathedral ceilings, custom furnishings, and a cool industrial / mid-century design that will make you feel like you stepped into a magazine. It’s a true penthouse spanning the whole top floor of the building. Here are a few things you will find if you stay here:  - Chef's kitchen with a gas range stove and grill. Complete with dishes, cutlery, and appliances (vitamix blender, rice cooker, toaster, hot water maker, coffee maker, le crusset wok, casserole dish, and pan)   - Den with a fully stocked library   - 2 West facing balconie","Hillcrest is a great neighborhood, it is quiet and safe and very close to a lot of fun San Diego activities. We are a 5 min walk to Balboa park and to tons of great restaurants. Little Italy, and Hillcrest are about 5 min away by car. Downtown is 7-10 minutes away, and we are just a 2 min drive to the 5 which will take you most anywhere you would want to go.",This is my home and I would ask that you treat it as such.  We love this place and want to share it with other cool and considerate guests. Please leave shoes at the door and make yourself at home.,I recommend just using Uber or Lyft or renting a car depending on how extensively you plan to travel.,,,While we want everyone to feel at home we request no more then 2 guests and would appreciate if you would leave your shoes at the door.,,1542783,https://www.airbnb.com/users/show/1542783,John,12/28/2011,"San Francisco, California, United States","Hi, my name is john, I lived in NYC for last 5 years but got a promotion to move to SF, i am very excited to try a new area and meet new people.  I am easy going, responsible and have perfect credit, references from past land lords and room mates.

Very interested to speak.

Cheers,

John ",,,,f,,1,1,t,t,"San Diego, CA, United States",Park West,Park West,San Diego,CA,92101,San Diego,"San Diego, CA",US,United States,32.73122,-117.16656,f,Loft,Entire home/apt,2,1,1,1,Real Bed,"{TV,Wifi,""Air conditioning"",Kitchen,""Paid parking off premises"",Elevator,""Free street parking"",""Indoor fireplace"",Heating,Washer,Dryer,""Smoke detector"",""Carbon monoxide detector"",Essentials,Shampoo,Hangers,""Hair dryer"",Iron,""Laptop friendly workspace"",""Self check-in"",Lockbox,""Luggage dropoff allowed"",""Long term stays allowed""}",,$300.00 ,$300.00 ,$500.00 ,$150.00 ,2,$150.00 ,3,1125,8,16,2/19/2018,9/3/2018,Very High,f,f,f,strict_14_with_grace_period,f,f
8771797,https://www.airbnb.com/rooms/8771797,1bed with shared bath,"private room,share bath with other student,free wifi,utilities included in the rent","Easy to get to bus stops to downtown, UCSD or Allant International University. Walking distance to shopping center. 步行可到公交车站,有开往UCSD的31路公交车､开往Downtown 的20路公交车和开往Alliant International University 的964路公交车｡步行可到商圈｡","private room,share bath with other student,free wifi,utilities included in the rent",Quiet but easy to get on freeway I-15,,Walking distance to the public transportation stops. And 2 minutes driving to I-15 freeway.,"Kitchen ,Free wifi ,free pool.",Please let me know if you need help,,,45508201,https://www.airbnb.com/users/show/45508201,Amy,10/1/2015,"San Diego, California, United States",I am a teacher friendly and easy going.,within an hour,100%,,f,Mira Mesa,3,3,t,f,"San Diego, CA, United States",Mira Mesa,Mira Mesa,San Diego,CA,92126,San Diego,"San Diego, CA",US,United States,32.90232,-117.12295,f,Guesthouse,Private room,1,1,1,1,Real Bed,"{TV,Wifi,Pool,Kitchen,""Free parking on premises"",Washer,Dryer,""Smoke detector"",Essentials,Shampoo,""Lock on bedroom door"",Hangers,""Hair dryer"",Iron,""Laptop friendly workspace"",""translation missing: en.hosting_amenity_49"",""translation missing: en.hosting_amenity_50"",""Hot water"",""Host greets you""}",,$45.00 ,$135.00 ,$0.00 ,$25.00 ,1,$10.00 ,3,1125,5,10,7/2/2017,5/27/2019,Very High,f,f,f,moderate,f,f
13746508,https://www.airbnb.com/rooms/13746508,Kennedy's SoCal Hideaway A Taste Of NYC Beachside,"Pet-friendly Beach Hideaway Steps To Sand, Dog Beach, Pier, And Downtown OB : ) A beautiful place to escape the trials of life, whether you're from inland San Diego/LA/OC, on the other side of the country, or across the world. Our hideaway is steps from everything OB has to offer: main beach, the famous pier, the dog beach, bars, restaurants, city bike rentals, surf shops and other shops on Newport Avenue. Come live the Oh Bee lifestyle : ) Central to all SD, near airport, beaches, and Seaworld!","Walk out the front door, down the alleyway, and within 25 yards you're on the main beach! If you're in the mood for a social beach day - then walk one step forward and you're in the sand - you made it!  If you're looking for something more laid back i.e. picturesque cliffs, restaurants, bars, shops, great people, and everything else Ocean Beach has to offer then just walk around your neighboring streets - congrats, you've arrived! ***UPDATE:  1. This property was upgraded and re-designed as of 02/19 2. We now offer pet-sitting nearby! If you come with your pets but still want to take in some of the local culture where pets may not be allowed, include some details about your furry friends and the dates you may need and we will try to accommodate!***","Pet-friendly Beach Hideaway Steps To Sand, Dog Beach, Pier, And Downtown OB : ) A beautiful place to escape the trials of life, whether you're from inland San Diego/LA/OC, on the other side of the country, or across the world. Our hideaway is steps from everything OB has to offer: main beach, the famous pier, the dog beach, bars, restaurants, city bike rentals, surf shops and other shops on Newport Avenue. Come live the Oh Bee lifestyle : ) Central to all SD, near airport, beaches, and Seaworld! Walk out the front door, down the alleyway, and within 25 yards you're on the main beach! If you're in the mood for a social beach day - then walk one step forward and you're in the sand - you made it!  If you're looking for something more laid back i.e. picturesque cliffs, restaurants, bars, shops, great people, and everything else Ocean Beach has to offer then just walk around your neighboring streets - congrats, you've arrived! ***UPDATE:  1. This property was upgraded and re-designed as of ","There is a convenience store, laundromat, gas station, bar, burger joint, 2 higher end restaurants, great breakfast spot, coffee shop, and liquor store all within a 5 minute walk of your front steps - need anything else? Just ask : )","1. There is a large, queen bed air mattress - you will need to push the kitchen tables and chairs into the kitchen in order to have enough floor space to set it up at night. This will limit access to kitchen and dining area but provides a comfortable bed vs. smaller less comfortable mattresses or cots. (BEWARE OF SCRAPING THE WALLS PLEASE) 2. The back patio and side yard are scheduled to be improved over the coming weeks, they are mostly empty at this time. 3. This is a close quarters duplex near the beach so noise can travel easily, be courteous and nicely ask for the same from the neighbors if necessary - everyone is pleasant as per the SD attitude : ) 4. NO CABLE, only internet enabled TV streaming 5. All of Ocean Beach is in the flight path of the airport's take-off routine. It is not terribly loud but it is noticeable. The official curfew is 11:30pm - 6:30am but Jet Blue, United, and Delta regularly break the curfew : / (Fly Southwest next time and keep OB quieter : ) 6. Outdoor s","1 dedicated parking spot out front and there is street parking available on nearby streets W. Point Loma Blvd, Muir Ave, and Voltaire Ave nearby bus stop for public transit, or city bikes for rent across the street!","You'll have full run of the bungalow and backyard area - great for pups to stretch and do their business - just kindly pick up after them : ) If you're going out for dinner or drinks while in the area, we highly recommend walking, renting City Bikes, or using Lyft - we can hook you up with a code to use if you're not familiar with it :)",We're avid texters so stay in touch : ),"- No shoes in house - Please NO parties, events, or loud noise after 10pm, very strict - Please no smoking inside but you can easily step outside (pick up your butts please) - All pets must be preapproved and fit in the following category: Non-vocal, light-shedding, potty-trained, non-chewers, and non-aggressive. Those that do are welcomed for shorter stays BUT they must stay with you when you leave, you cannot leave them behind for the day! (disoriented pets are loud pets) - NO PETS ON FURNITURE - If any rules are broken we reserve the right to withhold some or all of your deposit. Be nice and no worries : )",,80503950,https://www.airbnb.com/users/show/80503950,Jack,6/28/2016,"San Diego, California, United States",Hi there : ),within an hour,100%,,t,Ocean Beach,1,1,t,f,"San Diego, CA, United States",Ocean Beach,Ocean Beach,San Diego,CA,92109,San Diego,"San Diego, CA",US,United States,32.75357,-117.25062,t,Bungalow,Entire home/apt,6,1,1,3,Couch,"{TV,Wifi,Kitchen,""Free parking on premises"",""Pets allowed"",Heating,""Family/kid friendly"",""Smoke detector"",""Carbon monoxide detector"",Essentials,Shampoo,Hangers,""Hair dryer"",Iron,""Laptop friendly workspace"",""Private entrance"",Bathtub,""Baby bath"",""Hot water"",""Bed linens"",""Extra pillows and blankets"",Microwave,""Coffee maker"",Refrigerator,""Dishes and silverware"",""Cooking basics"",Oven,Stove,""Single level home"",""Patio or balcony"",""Garden or backyard"",""Long term stays allowed""}",,$95.00 ,$95.00 ,$500.00 ,$125.00 ,4,$10.00 ,1,1124,59,118,7/5/2016,7/28/2019,Average,f,t,f,strict_14_with_grace_period,f,f
5420666,https://www.airbnb.com/rooms/5420666,Residential rental 2BR 1bath ," (Website hidden by Airbnb)  beautiful and sunny upper unit with vaulted ceilings, spacious living room with fireplace. Open kitchen with breakfast bar, large master bedroom with ample closet space. Updated bathroom, washer/dryer. Nice place to relax in San Diego.   ",Sunny and cheerful," (Website hidden by Airbnb)  beautiful and sunny upper unit with vaulted ceilings, spacious living room with fireplace. Open kitchen with breakfast bar, large master bedroom with ample closet space. Updated bathroom, washer/dryer. Nice place to relax in San Diego.    Sunny and cheerful Close to I-15 Mira Mesa Exit for easy access to Downtown. Shopping and restaurants nearby. Perfect for the business person to relax after a day of work in San Diego. Adults preferred. Quiet peaceful area. Shade trees beside outdoor patio Neighbors respectfully quiet Covered parking Need to rent minimum of one month due to HOA restrictions.",Quiet peaceful area. Shade trees beside outdoor patio Neighbors respectfully quiet,Need to rent minimum of one month due to HOA restrictions.,Covered parking,Close to I-15 Mira Mesa Exit for easy access to Downtown. Shopping and restaurants nearby.,Perfect for the business person to relax after a day of work in San Diego. Adults preferred.,No smoking or pets No parties,,28102192,https://www.airbnb.com/users/show/28102192,Sharon,2/21/2015,"Colorado, United States",Semi retired RN. My husband and I love spending time in San Diego. We are only there part time.,,,,f,Scripps Ranch,1,1,t,f,"San Diego, CA, United States",Scripps Ranch,Scripps Ranch,San Diego,CA,92131,San Diego,"San Diego, CA",US,United States,32.92069,-117.11428,t,Condominium,Entire home/apt,4,1,2,2,Real Bed,"{TV,Internet,Wifi,""Air conditioning"",Pool,Kitchen,""Free parking on premises"",""Hot tub"",""Indoor fireplace"",Heating,Washer,Dryer,""Smoke detector"",""Carbon monoxide detector"",Essentials,Shampoo,Hangers,""Hair dryer"",