13997596,https://www.airbnb.com/rooms/13997596,The Bikini Bungalow,"The Bikini Bungalow is close to restaurants and dining, the beach & bay, & family-friendly activities. You’ll love my place because of the location, the people, and the ambiance. You cant beat the feeling of waking up in the morning and walking out your front door and hear the ocean waves crashing on the shore. My place is good for couples, families (with kids), big groups, and furry friends (pets) looking to get away and spend some time in a cute SoCal beach house.",The property has a large front patio that is very relaxing. It is a spacious two bedroom beach bungalow!,"The Bikini Bungalow is close to restaurants and dining, the beach & bay, & family-friendly activities. You’ll love my place because of the location, the people, and the ambiance. You cant beat the feeling of waking up in the morning and walking out your front door and hear the ocean waves crashing on the shore. My place is good for couples, families (with kids), big groups, and furry friends (pets) looking to get away and spend some time in a cute SoCal beach house. The property has a large front patio that is very relaxing. It is a spacious two bedroom beach bungalow! Bikes, beach equipment, laundry, bbq, large patio, boogie boards, beach towels, beach chairs I am available to guests via phone, text, or email. Beach, Bay, Belmont Park, Pacific Beach, Seaworld, Downtown, Airport, Ocean Beach, Balboa Park, The San Diego Zoo, and The Boardwalk. You can bike the boardwalk, walk, bike, or drive! This is such a great place to just leave your car parked once you arrive. This place is 30 yard","Beach, Bay, Belmont Park, Pacific Beach, Seaworld, Downtown, Airport, Ocean Beach, Balboa Park, The San Diego Zoo, and The Boardwalk.","This place is 30 yards from the beach, right across the street from the bay, and a walk to Belmont Park! It is an incredible location.  The area is very relaxing and less chaotic than other parts of Mission Beach.","You can bike the boardwalk, walk, bike, or drive! This is such a great place to just leave your car parked once you arrive.","Bikes, beach equipment, laundry, bbq, large patio, boogie boards, beach towels, beach chairs","I am available to guests via phone, text, or email.",Please take off shoes at door..leave sand outside :) No parties. No smoking.,,5190745,https://www.airbnb.com/users/show/5190745,Tess,2/22/2013,"San Diego, California, United States",I am simply just a family girl living life respectfully and to it's fullest. ,within an hour,100%,,f,Mission Beach,4,4,t,f,"San Diego, CA, United States",Mission Beach,Mission Bay,San Diego,CA,92109,San Diego,"San Diego, CA",US,United States,32.76266,-117.25144,t,Bungalow,Entire home/apt,8,2,2,5,Real Bed,"{TV,""Cable TV"",Internet,Wifi,Kitchen,""Free parking on premises"",""Pets allowed"",""Free street parking"",""Family/kid friendly"",Washer,Dryer,""Smoke detector"",""Carbon monoxide detector"",""First aid kit"",""Safety card"",""Fire extinguisher"",Essentials,Shampoo,""Lock on bedroom door"",Hangers,""Hair dryer"",Iron,""Laptop friendly workspace"",""Self check-in"",Keypad,""High chair"",""Pack ’n Play/travel crib"",""Hot water"",""Long term stays allowed""}",,$220.00 ,$660.00 ,$500.00 ,$115.00 ,8,$250.00 ,3,1124,27,54,6/4/2017,8/3/2019,Average,f,t,f,strict_14_with_grace_period,f,f
